		"excerpt": "We are excited to add four new data centers this week to Cloudflare's growing network, beginning with Colombo, Sri Lanka. This deployment is our 112th data center globally, and our 38th in Asia.\n\n",
		"feature_image": "https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/zkvhlag99gkb/3VTlpWUHnA0NwXkhd17fZh/2802819cddb3452d39dc78ffe5153809/colombo.png",
		"featured": false,
		"html": "\n            <figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card \">\n            \n            <Image src=\"https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/zkvhlag99gkb/gZ2qglqM8miZxSkvF5Gc4/fd77fdfffd6ebf00e46bfc6f36cadcdf/Colombo-112-01.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"kg-image\" width=\"3334\" height=\"1667\" loading=\"lazy\"/>\n            \n            </figure><p>We are excited to add four new data centers this week to Cloudflare&#39;s growing <a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/network/\">network</a>, beginning with Colombo, Sri Lanka. This deployment is our 112th data center globally, and our 38th in Asia.</p>\n    <div class=\"flex anchor relative\">\n      <h3 id=\"faster-performance\">Faster Performance</h3>\n      <a href=\"#faster-performance\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"relative sm:absolute sm:-left-5\">\n        <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentcolor\" d=\"m12.11 15.39-3.88 3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1-3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0-3.5l3.88-3.88a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-3.88 3.89a4.48 4.48 0 0 0 6.33 6.33l3.89-3.88a1 1 0 1 0-1.42-1.42Zm8.58-12.08a4.49 4.49 0 0 0-6.33 0l-3.89 3.88a1 1 0 0 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1 3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0 3.5l-3.88 3.88a1 1 0 1 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.89a4.49 4.49 0 0 0 0-6.33ZM8.83 15.17a1 1 0 0 0 1.1.22 1 1 0 0 0 .32-.22l4.92-4.92a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-4.92 4.92a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.42Z\"></path></svg>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n    \n            <figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card \">\n            \n            <Image src=\"https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/zkvhlag99gkb/7eujyLVeHS2HW2PNuXyV2B/d28784408615c9ae8bcfa7cbbc19e13f/SL_Tea-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"kg-image\" width=\"640\" height=\"428\" loading=\"lazy\"/>\n            \n            </figure><p>_<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/2.0/\">CC BY-NC-ND 2.0</a> <a href=\"https://flic.kr/p/bU5Loa\">image</a> by <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/lukecz/\">Pavel Dobrovsky</a>_</p><p>Six million Internet properties using Cloudflare are now even faster across the island country of Sri Lanka. Previously, local visitors to Cloudflare customers were served out of our <a href=\"/cloudflares-singapore-data-center-now-online/\">Singapore</a> or <a href=\"/middle-east-expansion/\">Dubai</a> data centers.</p>\n            <figure class=\"kg-card kg-image-card \">\n            \n            <Image src=\"https://cf-assets.www.cloudflare.com/zkvhlag99gkb/6mcIDWFEJhJOs1ihnyvTxe/ac8153fd1f7fb6e1219423ede548931c/SL_Latency-1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"kg-image\" width=\"736\" height=\"326\" loading=\"lazy\"/>\n            \n            </figure><p><i>Latency (ms) decreases 4x to Cloudflare customers.â€‚Source: </i><a href=\"https://www.cedexis.com/\"><i>Cedexis</i></a></p><p>Sri Lanka added over one million Internet users in the past year alone. At ~30% Internet penetration, there is considerable room to grow.</p>\n    <div class=\"flex anchor relative\">\n      <h3 id=\"next-three-cities\">Next Three Cities</h3>\n      <a href=\"#next-three-cities\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"relative sm:absolute sm:-left-5\">\n        <svg width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path fill=\"currentcolor\" d=\"m12.11 15.39-3.88 3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1-3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0-3.5l3.88-3.88a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-3.88 3.89a4.48 4.48 0 0 0 6.33 6.33l3.89-3.88a1 1 0 1 0-1.42-1.42Zm8.58-12.08a4.49 4.49 0 0 0-6.33 0l-3.89 3.88a1 1 0 0 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.88a2.52 2.52 0 0 1 3.5 0 2.47 2.47 0 0 1 0 3.5l-3.88 3.88a1 1 0 1 0 1.42 1.42l3.88-3.89a4.49 4.49 0 0 0 0-6.33ZM8.83 15.17a1 1 0 0 0 1.1.22 1 1 0 0 0 .32-.22l4.92-4.92a1 1 0 0 0-1.42-1.42l-4.92 4.92a1 1 0 0 0 0 1.42Z\"></path></svg>\n      </a>\n    </div>\n    <p>Our deployments to be revealed later this week will provide additional redundancy to existing facilities in North America and Africa.</p><p>If you enjoy the idea of helping build one of the world&#39;s largest networks, come <a href=\"https://www.cloudflare.com/careers/\">join our team</a>!</p>",
